Mitch Brooks.

218
00:11:50,911 --> 00:11:52,005
Oui. Ah bon ?

219
00:11:52,800 --> 00:11:54,205
Quel sandwich ?

220
00:11:55,966 --> 00:11:57,676
Je déconne. Je suis en attente.

221
